Really though, here's how it stacks up:

most of the other Preds are out+about.  (Starstorm/Perceptor/Flicker 
on their respective missions, Wolfenstein and Skulletron gone to the 
dark side, so to speak, and Phoenix captured.)  The only other people 
in the Pred base are Pumpskin and Vlad (still a prisoner).  The 
Maximals are involved in a somewhat testy alliance with the Rogues, 
mostly aimed at dealing with the newly beefed-up Tripred forces.  
Rodimus Prime and Nightlight have a new baby (hoo boy), other than 
that it's business as usual (which is always unusual).
